The types of content you need to make to succeed as a creatorpreneur⬇️

1. Short form content

IG, TikTok, Shorts.

Provide value, share testimonials, tell your story, transmit your personality.

Build a following, get new eyeballs on.

2. Long form

Provide value and nurture viewers further with long form content.

This is where the 7 hour rule comes into play.

3. Lead magnets

Provide freebies in return for contact information.

Trade notion templates, mini-courses, exclusive offers in order to build up a CRM and email list.

4. Story Strategy
 Communicate your message, personality and value through regular stories.

Include CTA’s at a 10:1 ratio to ensure an organic sales journey.

Implement these for sick results.

For more, comment ‘Creator’ for a free breakdown of exactly how to get started…
